cohortName: Acute respiratory failure referent incident cohort
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (319049) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: Acute respiratory failure referent prevalent cohort
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (319049) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history, with at least 365 days of prior continuous observation. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: Acute respiratory failure design diagnostics 1 cohort
logicDescription: Respiratory failure, arrest, hypoxemic respiratory failure, hypercapnic respiratory failure (with no descendants) added to acute respiratory failure with descendants
